text: Sofija Ņesterova (born 6 August 2001) is a Latvian footballer who plays as a goalkeeper for Sieviešu Futbola Līga club Rīgas FS and the Latvia women's national team. ==References== Category:2001 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football goalkeepers Category:Latvian women's footballers Category:Latvia women's international footballers Category:Rīgas FS players
